This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 910 Sq.
Tucked into a stunning landscape of mature trees and rolling green space, Aspire Apartments at Mountlake Terrace offers one and two bedroom apartment homes for rent just minutes from work and play.
Nearby access to I-5 and I-405 shrink your commute to major employers including Boeing and Premier Blue Cross, while neighborhood parks put outdoor adventure as close as your front door.
Come home to beautiful design and all the amenities at Aspire Apartments at Mountlake Terrace.
Interiors feature smart, energy-efficient appliances, and an in-home washer and dryer, as well as a spiral staircase, loft bedroom, and vaulted ceilings in select apartment homes.
Community advantages include a heated pool, spa, dry sauna, and impressively equipped fitness center.
The pup is sure to love our onsite dog park!
Experience the difference at Aspire Apartments at Mountlake Terrace, near Lynnwood.
